listing.name: Google Calendar + Trello Two-Way Sync
listing.description:
Unito allows you to connect Trello with Google Calendar in a 2-way sync to coordinate and plan timelines with team members by turning Trello cards into calendar events and vice versa.

“Unito is one of the best ways to sync data between Trello and any other tool. You keep using Trello — everyone else can use their thing.”
— Michael Pryor, co-founder, Trello


![Trello - Google Calendar Integration](https://unito.io/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/TrelloGCal.mp4.gif)

##Connect Trello to Google Calendar and keep teams looped on every project timeline

###This Power-Up is designed to help Trello users to:
- manage tasks for events or conferences; 
- operate a team roadmap or timeline; 
- share key business milestones;
- coordinate projects; 
- loop in other teams on deadlines with high visibility. 

Updates in one app are automatically reflected in the other based on deep, customizable rules determined by you. Unito workflows are quick, easy, and intuitive to build with our no-code interface so you can get up and running in minutes.

---
##Start a free 14-day trial now
Unito is free to try for 14 days, no credit card required. After that, you'll need to subscribe to one of our [paid plans](https://unito.io/pricing/?utm_source=trello&utm_medium=marketplace&utm_campaign=google_calendar).


## Features

### Unito supports essential Trello fields including: 

- Card names 
- Due dates and times 
- Assignees
- Card status and descriptions 
- Comments
- Labels
- List names
- Board names
- Attachments
- Checklists


### Share data in real-time

Automate the flow of information to and from Trello live. Changes in Google Calendar are immediately sent to your board and vice versa, based on the rules you choose.


### Experience a no-code, self-serve solution

Unito requires no coding knowledge whatsoever. Anyone on your team can integrate Trello with Google Calendar and start building the workflow they need in a few clicks through an intuitive point-and-click interface.


### Step-by-step walkthrough

Share milestones, launch dates, events and more between Trello and Google Calendar with Unito's automated 2-way sync. Here's a detailed guide on [how to sync Trello with Google Calendar to align Dates and Milestones](https://unito.io/blog/guide-how-to-trello-google-calendar/?utm_source=trello&utm_medium=marketplace&utm_campaign=trello_googlecalendar).

## What Unito customers are saying

“Unito saves us time we can use to pay attention to what really matters; solving our customers’ e-commerce challenges.” - Mark Lewis, CTO / Founder - Netalico Commerce

“Even if Unito just saves me two minutes per board, we’re opening and closing multiple transactions per day, it probably saves me 30 minutes per day. That adds up.” - Megan Baptista, Founder My TC Concierge 

“I have now ditched the bullet journal and moved fully online with the help of Unito. I can complete tasks on checklists, add comments, change due dates etc. without having to leave my main Trello board.” - Jessica Lorraine, Founder, Lorraine Virtual

---

Learn more about Unito's [Trello - Google Calendar integration](https://unito.io/connectors/trello/?utm_source=trello&utm_medium=marketplace&utm_campaign=trello_googlecalendar).

listing.name: Google Sheets + Trello 2-Way Sync
listing.description:
# Google Sheets + Trello 2-Way Sync
Sync Trello cards with Google Sheets rows using this powerful integration.

---
### Sync information from Trello into spreadsheets and get real-time insights on project performance in Google Sheets
With Unito, sync Trello cards to rows in Google Sheets and keep everything updated automatically. Build powerful reports in Google Sheets to get insights on progress in Trello with no manual work.

Unito also supports 2-way workflows, which means changes made in Google Sheets are synced back to your Trello cards. You can also use Unito to automatically create new Trello cards when a new row is created in Google Sheets. Unito helps keep everything in perfect sync across any workflow that needs Google Sheets and Trello..

![Trello - Google Sheets Integration](https://unito.io/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/TrelloSheets.mp4.gif)
### Features
#### Supports essential Trello fields
Unito has some of the deepest two-way integrations for Trello.. Sync card names, due dates, assignees, card status, card descriptions, comments, labels, list names, board names, attachments, checklists, and more. You can manually map these fields with any Google Sheets column and keep your data in sync.
#### Customize in real-time
Unito integrations allow data to flow across tools in real-time. Customize your flow to your exact needs and set powerful filters to define what you need synced. Make changes to your flow and they’ll be reflected in your tools in real-time.
#### No-code and self-serve
Unito requires no coding knowledge. Any team can integrate Trello with Google Sheets and build the workflow they need in a few clicks.

#### Some help to get started
Follow our detailed step-by-step guide to [learn how to connect your Trello board with a Google spreadsheet](https://unito.io/blog/guide-how-to-connect-trello-with-google-sheets/?utm_source=trello&utm_medium=marketplace&utm_campaign=trello_googlesheets), or watch our pre-recorded [demo video](https://vimeo.com/653097605).

---

![Michael Pryor tweet Unito](https://unito.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trello-Tweet.png)

**— Michael Pryor, Co-founder and Head of Product at Trello**

---
### Get started for free now!
Install the Power-Up and you’ll be taken through the setup process. Alternatively, you can also head directly to Unito to set up your account and get started!

Learn more about Unito's [Trello - Google Sheets integration](https://unito.io/integrations/google-sheets-trello/?utm_source=trello&utm_medium=marketplace&utm_campaign=trello_googlesheets).

![](https://api.segment.io/v1/pixel/track?data=ewogICJ3cml0ZUtleSI6ICJiQWpkVTg1ZnBIRDFyd2FEa1liZE1VTkZiaHgxelc4SSIsCiAgImFub255bW91c0lkIjogImFub255bW91c0lkIiwKICAiZXZlbnQiOiAiVmlzaXQgUG93ZXIgVXAiLAogICJwcm9wZXJ0aWVzIjogewogICAgInBvd2VyVXBOYW1lIjogIlN5bmMgd2l0aCBHb29nbGUgU2hlZXRzIiwKICAgICJ1cGRhdGVkQXQiOiAiMjAyMS0xMC0xOSIKICB9Cn0=)

listing.name: Google Диск
listing.description:
Благодаря улучшению «Google Диск» вы можете добавлять свои файлы и папки на карточки Trello. Выполняйте поиск, просматривайте уменьшенные версии файлов и переходите в Диск из Trello всего за один клик. А еще вы можете мгновенно превратить свою доску в презентацию Google.

— Используйте встроенный поиск, чтобы добавлять файлы и папки из Google Диска на карточки во всех версиях Trello.
— Открывайте уменьшенные версии прикрепленных файлов и папок и просматривайте сведения о них.
— Превращайте доску Trello в презентацию Google всего за один клик.

![скриншот](https://google-drive.trello.services/images/screenshots/Google_Drive_1.jpg)
![скриншот](https://google-drive.trello.services/images/screenshots/Google_Drive_2.jpg)
![скриншот](https://google-drive.trello.services/images/screenshots/Google_Drive_3.jpg)
![скриншот](https://google-drive.trello.services/images/screenshots/Google_Drive_4.jpg)
